<reference id="rrefcheckpointdbproc" xml:lang="pt-br">
<title>SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_CHECKPOINT_DATABASE</title>
<refbody>
<section>
<p>O procedimento do sistema
<codeph>SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_CHECKPOINT_DATABASE</codeph>
cria um ponto de controle no banco de dados, descarregando todos os dados
no <i>cache</i> para o disco.</p>
</section>
<section>
<title>Sintaxe</title>
<codeblock>SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_CHECKPOINT_DATABASE()</codeblock>
<p>Este procedimento n√£o retorna resultado.</p>
</section>
<section>
<title>Exemplo JDBC</title>
<codeblock>CallableStatement cs = conn.prepareCall
("CALL SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_CHECKPOINT_DATABASE()");
cs.execute();
cs.close();</codeblock>
</section>
<section>
<title>Exemplo SQL</title>
<codeblock>CALL SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_CHECKPOINT_DATABASE();</codeblock>
</section>
</refbody>
